Hi [Employee Name],

Hope you're having a great week!

Just wanted to follow up on our initial conversation and see how you're feeling about your upcoming relocation to London. We're excited to help make this transition as smooth as possible for you.

I've scheduled a call with our local expert, Sarah Miller, to discuss your housing needs in more detail. She has extensive knowledge of the London property market and can help you find the perfect place.

During the call, Sarah will go over your preferences, budget, and desired location. She'll also answer any questions you might have about neighborhoods, schools, transportation, and other important factors.

We've scheduled a property viewing for you with Sarah as well. Please see the details below.

Looking forward to connecting you with Sarah!

Best regards,

David Lee
Relocation Specialist
Global Mobility Solutions
